column5: went fishing on Scugog yesterday with my brother. We were hoping to catch some walleys...but ended up with a bunch of slabs. Majority of them were 12"-14"!!!! And we also caught enough sunfish to feed the entire town of Markham...LOL   a little bit exaggerated...but it was A LOT!!!!   . Unfortunately...we caught everything, but walley...Well...maybe I shouldn't say "unfortunate" because I caught a LOT OF FISH, and I had a lot of fun!!!! Yea it was a great day on the water...getting sun burn  lol
That's a nice slab you got there Jackie...
